Command: ./as2 -s 1024 1024 -f 4 -o examples/image-08.ppm examples/input-08
Runtime: 9.968s

Multiple light sources. The red/blue sphere are right above red/blue point lights. The platform in the middle blocks the two lights, giving a red-grey-blue pattern. Also one direction light source pointing downward to show how shadows from point lights are larger than the object.
